Class WEditorError

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.utils.wysiwyg.WEditorError
public class WEditorError extends Object
WYSIWYG Editor Error Contains information about an error that occurs somewhere in the WYSIWYG editor. This will usually be a MULTI error, but can be other things as well.
Author:
John L. Stanley - SRF Consulting, Gordon Parikh - SRF Consulting
